{"tid":816570,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【🌋樓爆2018】業主投降！🏳️德寶282呎上車盤大劈40萬至500萬成交！！","createTime":"2018-09-13T00:06:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-13T08:19:39.000Z","uid":43146,"like":3,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"7b54b60f6c4c87347b7509f9736e6d017bf20b91","tid":816570,"uid":43146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T00:06:23.000Z","msg":"樓市劈價風暴吹至東九。消息指，九龍灣得寶花園G座極高層7室「鳳凰樓」(頂樓之下一層)，向海，實用面積282方呎，叫價540萬元，剛減至500萬元易手，呎價17,730元。今年7月D座低層6室，望內園樓景，面積相同都賣520萬元，今次可謂「鳳凰樓」賣低層價。銀行估值更達571萬及592萬元，與估值比較，賣平最多92萬元或15%。<br />\n<br />\n細價樓近年升幅嚇人，得寶花園B座頂層連天台特色戶，實用面積254方呎，上月以543萬元成交，呎價逾2.1萬元。<br />\n<br />\n得寶花園上月底已重現「4字頭」成交。F座極高層3室「鳳凰樓」，實用面積282方呎，屬一房間隔，僅售485萬元，呎價17,199元。<br />\n<br />\n記者:朱連峰"},{"pid":"c24c01e607da587f60b9ef909175d9cf709c516f","tid":816570,"uid":52911,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T00:34:32.000Z","msg":"夠啦！唔好再貼喇！<br />\n每一日起身都比你提醒樓爆！<br />\n我個心好痛好想死呀！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我唔玩啦！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  原諒我啦 我唔做好友啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af111e31ff5f150bc000e8b483267fcadfb44703","tid":816570,"uid":52911,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T00:36:20.000Z","msg":"如果我一早聽班救世主講 我依家就可以安心租樓啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n樓主係咪想迫死我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52534d2911513542b525e21125af1052f0dcd4ec","tid":816570,"uid":89869,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T01:01:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/13/090111_078f19426ceec69d412e2aa582b830c8.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F13%2F